{"tid":83023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚老豆有事","createTime":"2017-01-16T11:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T15:56:14.000Z","uid":39513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ab453e5e99ab7c37230950af89bb3c4d4fafe9","tid":83023,"uid":39513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"話說今日我呀媽突然打比我<br />\n話我屋企門口有一男一女拎住公事包 係我地門口抄門牌<br />\n問我老豆咩事 佢又話無事無事 就走左去返工<br />\n好想知香港有咩人會抄門牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0836e58bc5659f5d5eb372c89d55cbb9cc0c9a","tid":83023,"uid":37753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"房署 財務公司 地產商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當年就係咁比人抄走左間公屋"},{"pid":"20c6b7faae458e637bb5eb3829b6e90da1ebfb4f","tid":83023,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:58:14.000Z","msg":"執達利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93740f4a0c2b30387b330868c65ba4c7eee5db2","tid":83023,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"你老豆唔會有事，係你成家有事"},{"pid":"705be22fff63a9e8b2681d55bbd9fa11bcb3f152","tid":83023,"uid":39513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>房署 財務公司 地產商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當年就係咁比人抄走左間公屋</blockquote><br />\n但我老豆唔會借錢 甚至都好少係屋企<br />\n我真係好驚老豆有做犯法野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255ae9c3d18b88fea058ddfce6158b91f96c944e","tid":83023,"uid":39513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆唔會有事，係你成家有事</blockquote><br />\n問佢又唔講 只係想知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c696a44a24caf04ff9e1f5a509328004155cf852","tid":83023,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:09:13.000Z","msg":"咁應該係大穫野喇 <br />\n小心你老豆走佬"},{"pid":"fb38773dbdfd36cf8abe4b1929dfb3d716c5784d","tid":83023,"uid":39513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁應該係大穫野喇 <br />\n小心你老豆走佬</blockquote><br />\n好撚不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f667ac1c3631e5a0c053b829cbee5bf3053c0e5","tid":83023,"uid":39513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:28:58.000Z","msg":"上左警局 了解事情 已經知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deed380d7d718a4101b92b0dd77c510e5d8264e9","tid":83023,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上左警局 了解事情 已經知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩事"},{"pid":"2bcd1a2eb1d55912d7273704b3467f4cbc68c489","tid":83023,"uid":7142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:36:07.000Z","msg":"快啲講咩事啦"},{"pid":"3a90738051f3cbcebde077b9af01cff4249b77ed","tid":83023,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啲講咩事啦</blockquote><br />\n好想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推到樓主講"},{"pid":"99a986a4f82a54cc728bdede4f2c3fbc2a992522","tid":83023,"uid":36417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a70ffff90e9093bbb5319d3318b557dbc8a2da1e","tid":83023,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>房署 財務公司 地產商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當年就係咁比人抄走左間公屋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351d